## Project Context

- **Client:** Chick-fil-A College Football Hall of Fame (cfbhall.com)
- **Agency work:** Client-shareable **search prototype** for presentation + Figma import later
- **This repo:** Static prototype — **NOT** production Umbraco
- **CMS target (later):** Umbraco Search / Examine index — **NO Search & Filter Pro**

---

## What We Are Building

1. Global header search — hours bar: always-visible input + crimson square; focus expands left; typeahead (not icon-only)
2. Predictive dropdown — HOF (avatar + team badge) vs general (text/icon)
3. `/search` page — query hero, **right** category filters, result cards, empty state
4. Mock Umbraco backend — local `search-index.json` (Examine-shaped documents)

---

## Tech Stack (do not change without asking)

- Prefer **vanilla HTML / CSS / JS**
- **No** React/Next, **No** Search & Filter Pro
- Fonts: Kaneda + Neusa Next — **not Inter / Roboto / Arial as brand faces**

### Brand tokens (locked from live site)

| Token role | Live value |
|---|---|
| Primary CTA / accent | `#b5202b` / `#b5212a` crimson |
| Chrome | **White** left sidebar; border `#C0C1C3` |
| Hours / dark strips | Black `#000000` |
| Muted UI text | `#888A8E` |
| Display font | Kaneda (condensed uppercase) |
| Body / UI font | Neusa Next / Neusa Next Std Compact |
| Avoid | Inter; amber/gold SaaS accents; indigo; navy top-bar |

---

## Umbraco Mimic (required pattern)

One shared dataset for typeahead **and** results: `data/search-index.json`

Fields: `id`, `docType`, `category`, `title`, `excerpt`, `url`, `image`, `date`  
Inductees also: `inductionYear`, `team`, `teamBadge`

Categories (locked): `all` | `inductees` | `news` | `events` | `general-tickets`

