## What NOT To Do

- Do not rebuild the full CFHF marketing site
- Do not invent a navy horizontal global header
- Do not use gold as a system brand color
- Do not add Search & Filter Pro or Umbraco packages
- Do not leave Inter + amber/gold as the client-facing brand
- Do not force-push `master` or skip hooks

